review: Dr. Swetha has been a guiding doctor from the beginning of my conception. It's through her have got the exact protocols. She communicates clearly on the problem/ health issues and treatment method. Approachable and patient friendly. I have already recommended to my friends, neighbours and family members.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,
review:
Accompanied my wife as she is suffering from improper menstrual cycle. Booked an appointment through Practo app for 11:30am. Doctor came in at 11:55am. Expected doctor availability as per Practo booking, this is an improvement area.
With regards to Doctor's ********** experience and conduct, it was a positive experience.
She is knowledgeable, friendly, has patience, allows you to explain your problem patiently and prescribes practical solution.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Wait time,
context: Pregnancy Check Up,Normal Vaginal Delivery (NVD),Pre and Post Delivery Care,
review:
I visited doctor for my second pregnancy. The care of the doctor was excellent. 

During my delivery it was late night full of raining. Doctor visited the hospital for delivery, the delivery of mine was unforgettable and the Dr.Shwetha saved me and my kid... Thanks for her responsibility and caring.

I recommend Dr.Shwetha for all of my friends and family.

All the staff, room service of motherhood was also good.

review: My wife had been having irregular periods for few months. we visited aikya clinic and doctor prescribed some tests from another diagonastic centre. we got it done. she said everything looks normal and gave tablets for a course of 21 days to take every night. ***** *** ** ****** ** we visited the doctor back. she simply said continue the same tablet for 3 months untill it works. it's been more than 4 months *** **** *** ******** I don't know if anyone can be asked to wait for such long time. anyhow, considering to visit another doctor now.time and money wasted

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
The Dr is very young, initially I had doubts , but surprisingly she is more experienced than she looks , she is really friendly and cares for the patients a lot and always encouraged to be confident throughout the pregnancy, she never created a doubt for me to have a second opinion , she built so much of trust , she help me deliver through normal delivery , I had so much difficulty during delivery she was there and kept on encouraging to make sure I deliver through normal delivery.
Surprising to see such doctors these days
Thanks you so much Dr Swetha.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review:
Many of your patients have recommended you as a good doctor. But I am going one step further to also to recommend you as a great human being. 

Delivering my latest baby was much easier than I anticipated. Thank you for coming to the hospital even when you were sick,  to deliver my baby RUTVIKA. I was very glad to have you there since you‚Äôve been caring for me since the start the pregnancy. Your easy going manner helped me to relax. I am glad everything went so well!
¬†
No words are enough to appreciate the service you do. Thank you for all your service.
